The impressive feat of Herb Jones, a New Orleans Pelicans player, is recognized as he makes NBA history with his All-Defense honor. Overall, these headlines highlight the multifaceted nature of herbs, from culinary delights to health remedies and even their role in the realm of sports.

summary: Multiple news sources are reporting on an incident involving singer Kelly Rowland and a security guard at the Cannes Film Festival. Rowland was reportedly rushed up the stairs at the "Marcello Mio" premiere when she appeared to have a confrontation with the usher. A lip reader has since revealed that Rowland told the guard, "You guys are crazy." The incident has sparked controversy, with many speculating about the cause of the exchange. Some sources claim that Rowland was upset at being pushed and rushed, while others suggest that she may have been frustrated by the heavy security presence at the event. Rowland has not yet commented publicly on the incident.

name: Florida Panthers
summary: The Florida Panthers have advanced to the Eastern Conference Finals of the 2024 Stanley Cup playoffs after defeating the Boston Bruins in Game 6 with a late game-winning goal. This marks their second consecutive appearance in the Eastern Conference Finals. The Panthers will now face the New York Rangers in a best-of-seven series starting on Friday. The Rangers also advanced after defeating the Boston Bruins in Game 6 of their series. Game 1 of the Eastern Conference Finals between the Panthers and Rangers will be played in New York on Friday, May 5th.

name: Orioles vs Cardinals
summary: The series between the Baltimore Orioles and St. Louis Cardinals has been affected by weather, with the game on May 22 being delayed due to rain, and the game on May 21 being suspended. The games were eventually scheduled for a doubleheader on May 23, with the first game starting in the morning and the second in the evening. Despite the weather delays, the Cardinals managed to secure a 3-1 victory on May 21, with Nolan Gorman contributing a home run. The Cardinals are favored to win the upcoming doubleheader, with the Orioles experiencing a recent losing streak.

name: Inside the NBA
summary: Several articles discuss the potential end of the popular NBA analysis show "Inside the NBA" on TNT as NBC reportedly nears a deal to acquire exclusive NBA rights. The cast of "Inside the NBA" recently won three Sports Emmys and made headlines for unanimously picking the Minnesota Timberwolves over the Dallas Mavericks in a playoff matchup. Amidst rumors of the show's conclusion, Charles Barkley has expressed concerns about the financial implications and the impact on the show's beloved crew. Various outlets speculate on the future of "Inside the NBA" and the potential for NBC to offer compelling alternatives.
